							#navDetail1-1.tab-pane.fade.show.active( role='tabpanel' ) Intense gives you a variety of powerful options, useful tools, and unlimited designs to easily create a website of your dreams that your clients will love.
							#navDetail1-2.tab-pane.fade( role='tabpanel' ) Use the built-in slider plugins to create appealing blocks with smooth sliders that are completely responsive and customizable.
							#navDetail1-3.tab-pane.fade( role='tabpanel' ) Change the layout of Intense with the included content blocks ranging from counters to tabs and accordions and other impressive elements.
